# Strict folder protection: Only allow canonical documentation files
# Reject all other files to maintain documentation cleanliness

# Deny all files by default
*

# Exception: Allow canonical files
!backlog.md
!release-notes.md
!vision.md
!github-action.md
!cloud-deployment.md

# API Contracts
!api/swagger.yaml
!api/mock_data.json

# Rules
!rules/habits.md
!rules/hygiene.md
!rules/decisions.md

# Standards
!standards/ultra-lean.md

# Directories
!api/
!rules/
!standards/

# Allow .gitignore itself
!.gitignore
